# Privotron – optional environment variables
#
# Privotron itself does not require env vars for basic use. This template
# exists so the stack has a consistent .env entry point.
#
# Copy to stack.env if you want to pin a specific Privotron version or set TZ.

# TZ/locale: use shared.env (see documents/SHARED-RESOURCES.md)

# Optional: build Privotron from a specific branch/tag instead of main.
# Example: PRIVOTRON_VERSION=v1.0
# PRIVOTRON_VERSION=main

